        <Meaning id="c98837b2-dc8b-42c5-be1f-eb6933b88d33" type="Adverb">
          <Vi>gần gũi; một cách chặt chẽ; một cách kỹ lưỡng</Vi>
          <En>In a close manner; with little space or distance between things; with careful attention or scrutiny.</En>
          <Example>She examined the document closely to spot any errors.</Example>
          <IsArchaic>false</IsArchaic>
          <Situations>
            <Situation id="493711e0-dbc1-493d-a525-603c4f3b1e46">
